<!-- Definition and symptoms -->
'''間皮瘤'''（Mesothelioma）是一種源自於覆蓋內臟表面的薄層組織（[[間皮細胞|間皮細胞]]）的[[癌症|癌症]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Malignant Mesothelioma—Patient Version|url=http://www.cancer.gov/types/mesothelioma|website=NCI|accessdate=2016-04-03|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406195227/http://www.cancer.gov/types/mesothelioma|archivedate=2016-04-06|date=January 1980}}</ref>。最常患病的部位是[[胸膜|胸膜]]<ref name=NCI2015Pt>{{cite web|title=Malignant Mesothelioma Treatment–Patient Version (PDQ®)|url=http://www.cancer.gov/types/mesothelioma/patient/mesothelioma-treatment-pdq|website=NCI|accessdate=2016-04-03|date=2015-09-04|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405125547/http://www.cancer.gov/types/mesothelioma/patient/mesothelioma-treatment-pdq|archivedate=2016-04-05}}</ref><ref name=Rob2012/>。[[腹膜|腹膜]]也有，但較少見。在罕見的情下會出現在[[心包|心包膜]]<ref name=Sar2012>{{cite journal|last1=Sardar|first1=MR|last2=Kuntz|first2=C|last3=Patel|first3=T|last4=Saeed|first4=W|last5=Gnall|first5=E|last6=Imaizumi|first6=S|last7=Lande|first7=L|title=Primary pericardial mesothelioma unique case and literature review.|journal=Texas Heart Institute Journal / From the Texas Heart Institute of St. Luke's Episcopal Hospital, Texas Children's Hospital|date=2012|volume=39|issue=2|pages=261–4|pmid=22740748|pmc=3384041}}</ref>或{{le|睪丸鞘膜|tunica vaginalis}}<ref name=NCI2015Pt/><ref name=Pan2015>{{cite journal|last1=Panou|first1=V|last2=Vyberg|first2=M|last3=Weinreich|first3=UM|last4=Meristoudis|first4=C|last5=Falkmer|first5=UG|last6=Røe|first6=OD|title=The established and future biomarkers of malignant pleural mesothelioma.|journal=Cancer Treatment Reviews|date=June 2015|volume=41|issue=6|pages=486–95|pmid=25979846|doi=10.1016/j.ctrv.2015.05.001}}</ref>。間皮瘤的症狀有因{{le|肋膜積液|pleural effusion|肺中液體瀦留}}造成的[[呼吸困難|呼吸困難]]、腹部腫脹、胸壁疼痛、咳嗽、疲倦，以及體重減輕<ref name=NCI2015Pt/>。這些症狀出現的速度一般而言較為緩慢<ref name=Kon2016/>。

<!-- 成因、病生理學及診斷 -->
超過80%的間皮瘤是由暴露在含[[石棉|石棉]]的環境中所導致的<ref name=Rob2012/>。暴露程度越高，風險越大<ref name=Rob2012>{{cite journal|last1=Robinson|first1=BM|title=Malignant pleural mesothelioma: an epidemiological perspective.|journal=Annals of Cardiothoracic Surgery|date=November 2012|volume=1|issue=4|pages=491–6|pmid=23977542|doi=10.3978/j.issn.2225-319X.2012.11.04|pmc=3741803}}</ref>。截至2013年，約有1.25億人曾在工作環境中接觸石棉<ref name=Gul2015/>。患病比例較高的族群有：石棉礦的礦工、將石棉加工製做成產品的人、工作時會接觸石棉製品的人、和以上這些人同住的人，以及在含有石棉的建築物中工作的人<ref name=Rob2012/>。從暴露石棉到癌症出現大約相隔40年<ref name=Rob2012/>。清洗石棉工作者的衣物也會增加清洗者的罹病風險<ref name=Gul2015>{{cite journal|last1=Gulati|first1=M|last2=Redlich|first2=CA|title=Asbestosis and environmental causes of usual interstitial pneumonia.|journal=Current Opinion in Pulmonary Medicine|date=March 2015|volume=21|issue=2|pages=193–200|pmid=25621562|doi=10.1097/MCP.0000000000000144|pmc=4472384}}</ref>。其他風險因子包含[[遗传|遗传]]以及被[[SV40|SV40]]病毒感染<ref name=Rob2012/>。間皮瘤可以用[[胸部X光|胸部X光]]及[[X射线计算机断层成像|X射线计算机断层成像]]進行初步診斷，再用[[細胞生物學|細胞生物學]]或是[[活體組織切片|活體組織切片]]來確診<ref name=Kon2016/>。

<!-- 預防及治療 -->
預防的重點為減少石棉暴露<ref name=Whit2006>{{cite book|last1=Whittemore|first1=Alice S.|title=Cancer epidemiology and prevention|date=2006|publisher=Oxford University Press|location=Oxford|isbn=9780199747979|page=669|edition=3rd|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qfN8Y1_lbDYC&pg=PA669|access-date=2020-03-08|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307062911/https://books.google.com/books?id=qfN8Y1_lbDYC&pg=PA669|dead-url=no}}</ref>。間皮瘤的治療通常包括手術、[[放射線療法|放射線療法]]，及[[化學療法|化學療法]]<ref name=NCI2015PtTx/>。有一種稱為[[肋膜黏連術|肋膜黏連術]]的術式，是用[[滑石|滑石]]之類的物質使[[胸膜|胸膜]]產生疤痕並沾黏在一起，可用來防止肺部積水增加<ref name=NCI2015PtTx>{{cite web|title=Malignant Mesothelioma Treatment–Patient Version (PDQ®)|url=http://www.cancer.gov/types/mesothelioma/patient/mesothelioma-treatment-pdq#section/_50|website=NCI|accessdate=2016-04-03|date=2015-09-04|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405125547/http://www.cancer.gov/types/mesothelioma/patient/mesothelioma-treatment-pdq#section/_50|archivedate=2016-04-05}}</ref>。化療一般會用[[順鉑|順鉑]]及{{le|培美曲塞|pemetrexed}}<ref name=Kon2016>{{cite journal|last1=Kondola|first1=S|last2=Manners|first2=D|last3=Nowak|first3=AK|title=Malignant pleural mesothelioma: an update on diagnosis and treatment options.|journal=Therapeutic Advances in Respiratory Disease|date=2016-02-12|pmid=26873306|pmc=5933604|doi=10.1177/1753465816628800|volume=10|issue=3|pages=275–88}}</ref>。在美國，患者的[[五年存活率|五年存活率]]平均而言為8%<ref name=SEER2016>{{cite web|title=Age-Adjusted SEER Incidence and U.S. Death Rates and 5-Year Relative Survival (Percent) By Primary Cancer Site, Sex and Time Period|url=http://seer.cancer.gov/archive/csr/1975_2011/results_merged/topic_survival.pdf|website=NCI|accessdate=2016-04-03|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906195701/http://seer.cancer.gov/archive/csr/1975_2011/results_merged/topic_survival.pdf|archivedate=2015-09-06}}</ref>。

<!-- Epidemiology and prognosis -->
在2015年，約有60800人罹患間皮瘤，其中32000人因此死亡<ref name=GBD2015Pre>{{cite journal|last1=GBD 2015 Disease and Injury Incidence and Prevalence|first1=Collaborators.|title=Global, regional, and national incidence, prevalence, and years lived with disability for 310 diseases and injuries, 1990-2015: a systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2015.|journal=Lancet|date=2016-10-08|volume=388|issue=10053|pages=1545–1602|pmid=27733282|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(16)31678-6|pmc=5055577}}</ref><ref name=GBD2015De>{{cite journal|last1=GBD 2015 Mortality and Causes of Death|first1=Collaborators.|title=Global, regional, and national life expectancy, all-cause mortality, and cause-specific mortality for 249 causes of death, 1980-2015: a systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2015.|journal=Lancet|date=2016-10-08|volume=388|issue=10053|pages=1459–1544|pmid=27733281|doi=10.1016/s0140-6736(16)31012-1|pmc=5388903}}</ref>。世界各地的間皮瘤發生率依地區而不同<ref name=Rob2012/>，在澳洲及英國的發生率較高，在日本則較低<ref name=Rob2012/>。在美國，每年約有3000個人得到此病<ref>{{cite web|title=What are the key statistics about malignant mesothelioma?|url=http://www.cancer.org/cancer/malignantmesothelioma/detailedguide/malignant-mesothelioma-key-statistics|website=American Cancer Society|accessdate=2016-04-03|date=2016-02-17|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408094758/http://www.cancer.org/cancer/malignantmesothelioma/detailedguide/malignant-mesothelioma-key-statistics|archivedate=2016-04-08}}</ref>，男性得到此病的比率比女性高<ref name=Rob2012/>。自1950年起，此病的發生率便呈現上昇的趨勢<ref name=Rob2012/>。被診斷出此病時病患大多年過65，且大多在七十歲左右死亡<ref name=Rob2012/>。在石棉的商業化應用問世以前，這個疾病非常罕見<ref name=Rob2012/>。
